---
const stats = [
  {
    name: 'Experts',
    value: '1',
  },
  {
    name: 'Years',
    value: '15',
  },
  {
    name: 'Projects',
    value: '250+',
  },
  {
    name: 'Awards',
    value: '3',
  },
];
---


<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <!-- Mission description -->
        <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12 lg:mt-2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Gold Coast Outdoor Tiling Experts</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">Elevate Your Outdoor Space with Golden Tiling's Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Welcome to Golden Tiling's Outdoor Tiling page, where we specialize in transforming ordinary outdoor areas 
              into extraordinary outdoor sanctuaries. Your outdoor space is an extension of your home, and we believe it 
              should be a reflection of your style, taste, and personality. Whether you have a patio, a garden terrace, a 
              poolside deck, or any other outdoor area, we are here to turn your vision into a reality.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">Gold Coast's Premier Outdoor Tiling Specialists</h3>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Golden Tiling has established itself as Gold Coast's premier outdoor tiling specialist, known for exceptional 
              craftsmanship, creative design, and a commitment to quality. Our dedicated team of professionals understands 
              the unique challenges that outdoor tiling presents, from weather resistance to slip resistance. We work closely 
              with you to select the perfect tiles, patterns, and layouts that not only enhance the aesthetics of your outdoor 
              space but also ensure its functionality and longevity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 mt-20">
        

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
          <!-- Mission description -->
          <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">Pool Tiling Solutions</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
                Welcome to Golden Tiling, where we turn your pool area into a luxurious oasis that mirrors the stunning landscapes of the Gold Coast. 
                Our Pool Tiling page is your gateway to discovering the perfect blend of style, safety, and durability for your swimming pool. 
                With a passion for perfection and a reputation for excellence, we are your trusted partners in transforming your pool into a masterpiece.
              </p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">Design your Pool Paradise</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
                The Gold Coast's abundant sunshine and beautiful coastline make pool areas an integral part of our outdoor living. 
                At Golden Tiling, we understand the unique demands and opportunities that pool tiling presents. Our team of skilled 
                professionals is dedicated to creating not just a pool but a paradise that reflects your personal style. We offer a 
                wide range of exquisite tile options, from slip-resistant materials for safety to elegant designs that elevate your pool's aesthetics.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full my-16">
    <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
      {
        stats.map((stat) => (
          <div class="border-primary-900/10 dark:border-primary-300/10 rounded-3xl border p-6">
            <dt class="text-base">{stat.name}</dt>
            <dd class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight">{stat.value}</dd>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

